<h1 class="stdPage__title">CBR in the News</h1>

<h3 class="stdPage__summary">Centre Building was completed in June 2019, six years after LSE selected world renowned architects Rogers Stirk Harbour + Partners (RSHP) as designers of the School's largest project.</h3>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<div class="slice--light">
<div class="container">
<div class="column__4 mediumColumn__3 colL">

<p>&nbsp;</p>

</div>
<div class="column__4 mediumColumn__8 largeColumn__8">
<div class="pageContent pageContent--std">



<section class="accordion"><a class="accordion__trigger" href="one"><header class="accordion__header">
<h2 class="accordion__title">2022</h2>
</header></a>
<div class="accordion__panel">
<div class="accordion__content">

<p>Richard Rogers, the founder of Rogers Stirk Harbour and Partners (RSHP) the architects who designed the LSE Centre Building, sadly passed away shortly before Christmas.&nbsp;<a class="sys_16" href="https://londonschoolofeconomicscommunications.newsweaver.com/staffnews/vx0mn31513n1wx40n5ubb9?email=true&amp;lang=en&amp;a=5&amp;p=8933284&amp;t=3345397"> Read a tribute to Richard here</a></p>

</div>
</div>
</section>



<section class="accordion"><a class="accordion__trigger" href="one"><header class="accordion__header">
<h2 class="accordion__title">2021</h2>
</header></a>
<div class="accordion__panel">
<div class="accordion__content">

<p><strong>The Architecture Club, 26 July 2021&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p><a title="https://www.architectureclub.co.uk/events/centre-building" class="sys_16" onclick="void(window.open('https://www.architectureclub.co.uk/events/centre-building','','toolbar=yes,menubar=yes,location=yes,scrollbars=yes,status=yes,resizable=yes'));return false;" onkeypress="void(window.open('https://www.architectureclub.co.uk/events/centre-building','','toolbar=yes,menubar=yes,location=yes,scrollbars=yes,status=yes,resizable=yes'));return false;" href="https://www.architectureclub.co.uk/events/centre-building">Centre Building</a></p>
